<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٥٣٠⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عائشة <span class="c2">(و)</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span> سئلت عن أدب اليتيم فقالت: <span class="c2">(إني)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> لأضرب أحدهم حتى <span class="c2">(ينبسط)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
